Package author: Igor Gaponenko

Brief description:
==================

The persistent database-driven Authorization service for Web applications.

The package contains:

  - database schema for MySQL
  - database schema initialization script
  - command-line python application for managing the contents
    of the database from UNIX shells
  - PHP library for Web applications
  - reference Web application for managing the contents of the database

